(106,0,'2020-07-31 00:00:00','2020-07-31 00:00:00','Plant-based whole-foods, zero plastic business since 2012. MANA! SoHo - 8 Staunton Street, SoHo is now open!<br />\n<br />\nLoving the outdoor signs #dietchangenotclimatechange we did for MANA!&#x27;s new location at SoHo. And we always appreciate how MANA! is always leading us in making our world a better place.<br />\n<br />\nIndoor we created 4 neon signage with environmental friendly messages designed by MANA!&#x27;s team. MANA! has been innovating their way towards Zero Waste since 2012, turning over 4 tonnes of food scraps and all of MANA!’s compostable packaging into soil compost every month.<br />\n<br />\nMANA! SoHo - 8 Staunton Street, SoHo<br />\n<br />\n#MANAHK #ItsGoodToBeHere #FoodThatDoesntCostTheEarth','MANA! SoHo','','publish','open','open','','mana-soho','','','2020-07-31 00:00:00','2020-07-31 00:00:00','',0,'http://113.253.77.204:8080/mana-soho/',0,'post','',0),
