(110,0,'2020-04-20 00:00:00','2020-04-20 00:00:00','Green Monday x TREATS 期間限定店已經登陸太古城啦！期間限定店每逢星期五至日亦將舉辦試食活動及產品推廣活動；於店內指定位置掃描遊戲QR code，答中所有問題者，有機會獲得精美獎品！除此之外，期間限定店更備有一輛單車充電裝置，顧客可以踏單車的形式為自己的電話充電，環保又健康！<br />\n<br />\n日期：即日起至12月2日<br />\n地址：太古太古城道18號太古城中心二期2樓255號舖<br />\n<br />\nThere will be food sampling and promotion every Friday to Sunday throughout the period. You can scan game QR code at the store designated location, simply the answer the questions correctly and you will stand a chance to get an exquisite prize from Green Monday! What&#x27;s more, there is a charging bicycle at the pop-up store for consumers to charge their mobile phone in a fun and sustainable way!<br />\n<br />\nPeriod：From now on till 2nd December<br />\nAddress：255 2/F, Cityplaza Phase 3, 11 2, 14 Tai Koo Wan Rd, Taikoo<br />\n<br />\n#gogreen #makechangehappen #greenmonday #vegan #vegetarian #climiatechange #healthy #igfood #foodstagram #sustainability #taikoo','GREEN MONDAY ⨉ TREATS','','publish','open','open','','green-monday-%e2%a8%89-treats','','','2020-04-20 00:00:00','2020-04-20 00:00:00','',0,'http://113.253.77.204:8080/green-monday-%e2%a8%89-treats/',0,'post','',0),
