(124,0,'2020-02-29 00:00:00','2020-02-29 00:00:00','MLY Behind the Art: &quot;Over the past decades, Mary was always there to heal thousands of loneliness selves.  Sadly with the uprise of various technology, we start forgetting about her.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThis showcases the lonely journey of Mary.  The idea of this illustration is arousing to the loneliness that they are not alone.  Mary will be here for us anywhere, anytime. It’s time to inflate the perfect date again!<br />\n<br />\nWebsite: https://www.marylovesu.com/<br />\n<br />\nOnline Store: https://teespring.com/en-GB/stores/marylovesyou<br />\n<br />\nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/marylovesyoustore/','Mary Loves You・Pop-Up Gallery','','publish','open','open','','mary-loves-you%e3%83%bbpop-up-gallery','','','2020-02-29 00:00:00','2020-02-29 00:00:00','',0,'http://113.253.77.204:8080/mary-loves-you%e3%83%bbpop-up-gallery/',0,'post','',0),
