(126,0,'2019-11-30 00:00:00','2019-11-30 00:00:00','早前為連卡佛多個分店做了數個的霓虹燈牌，以假日派對為主題的，超有聖誕時的節日氣氛。主打 Slogan 「GREATEST PARTY HITS」就是要把自己打造成由頭到腳尖都型格動人的假日潮流指標！我們做的燈牌還有是放到派對造型廚窗的「PARTY HITS」和永遠女性們最愛的美妝部的「BEAUTY HITS」，令顧客們在充滿聖誕色彩的 Lane Crawford 購得盡興！<br />\n<br />\n「GREATEST PARTY HITS」is the theme of Lane Crawford&#x27;s Christmas Campaign 2019, meaning to outfit yourself from top-to-toe with our fabulous edit for the festive season! We created neon signs in branch shops, bring the best Christmas vibe to every customers. We are loving our &quot;PARTY HITS&quot; neon sign at the party wardrobe themed window display, as well as the &quot;BEAUTY HITS&quot; neon at the cosmetics and beauty section!','LANE CRAWFORD Party Hits 2019','','publish','open','open','','lane-crawford-party-hits-2019','','','2019-11-30 00:00:00','2019-11-30 00:00:00','',0,'http://113.253.77.204:8080/lane-crawford-party-hits-2019/',0,'post','',0),
