(134,0,'2019-08-31 00:00:00','2019-08-31 00:00:00','很榮幸能為 Spotify 在新加玻舉行的 Spotify Supper 活動做這個霓虹燈。跳出了 Spotify 原品牌的綠色調，今次藉著活動為大眾介紹這個新粉紅色調，掛在舞台上更有新鮮感更搶眼。<br />\n<br />\nA fantastic night in Singapore at the Spotify Supper. Loving our neon sign on stage! Introducing Spotify new brand color with our pink neon flex, refreshing and bold new brand identity.','Spotify Supper @ Singapore','','publish','open','open','','spotify-supper-singapore','','','2019-08-31 00:00:00','2019-08-31 00:00:00','',0,'http://113.253.77.204:8080/spotify-supper-singapore/',0,'post','',0),
